      <p>Clicking the ‘Validate’ button will highlight cells with spelling mistakes, formatting errors and missing required values (<xref rid="F3" ref-type="fig">Fig. 3</xref>). The ‘Next Error’ button enables users to toggle between highlighted cells to correct errors. The button disappears when all errors have been addressed. The version of the DataHarmonizer used to perform curation is captured upon validation in the ‘DataHarmonizer Provenance’ field.</p>
